name: CutieContest
description:
Hello Players, thanks for playing this game. I want to say thanks to my friends Ahnon and Ofenstichloch for contributing in this game. Tutorial:

1. Take Part in a CutieContest to earn Cutie Coins and Rank up in the ladder

2. Buy Cutifier to get better chances at winning the contest

3. Buy more Cuties

4. Profit

If you send me more Cutie Pictures I will add them to the game :D
